          RELEASE NOTES:

          With a priceless artifact as your guide, you and Addie lead an
        expedition of stalwart explorers through long forgotten lands.
        These explorers are relying on you to create campsites for them
        to stay safe and warm as they brave the unknown. Relive the
        artifact's tale of an ancient civilization as they travelled to
        sandy beaches, through dense jungles, over high mountains and
        deep into mysterious caves. Encounter quirky characters, discover
        hidden treasures and rebuild ancient structures. Can you find
        what lies at the end of the artifact's tale? Find out in
        Campgrounds: The Endorus Expedition, a new and exciting Time
        Management game!
